graph LR
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>v1.21.0-18]

    %% External Dependencies (Runtime)
    ODHDashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 20.x]
    ODHDashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18.2.0]
    ODHDashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6.3.1]
    ODHDashboard -->|backend framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1]
    ODHDashboard -->|K8s API client| K8sClientNode[kubernetes/client-node 0.12.2]
    ODHDashboard -->|build tooling| Webpack[Webpack 5.96.1]
    ODHDashboard -->|state mgmt| Redux[Redux 4.2.0]
    ODHDashboard -->|routing| ReactRouter[React Router 7.6.2]
    ODHDashboard -->|auth proxy| OAuthProxy[OpenShift OAuth Proxy]
    ODHDashboard -.->|optional metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    ODHDashboard -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    ODHDashboard -->|authentication| OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    ODHDashboard -->|ingress| OSRouter[OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Components)
    ODHDashboard -->|reads config| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster, DSCInitialization]
    ODHDashboard -->|manages notebooks| KubeflowNB[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CR]
    ODHDashboard -->|reads serving status| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService CR]
    ODHDashboard -->|manages registries| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CR]
    ODHDashboard -->|serving runtimes| ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>ServingRuntime CR]
    ODHDashboard -->|workbench mgmt| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebook instances]
    ODHDashboard -->|pipeline integration| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Pipeline Runs, Experiments]
    ODHDashboard -->|bias metrics| TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service<br/>Bias and Fairness]
    ODHDashboard -->|workload queues| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Workload Queue Config]
    ODHDashboard -->|distributed training| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>Distributed Workloads]
    ODHDashboard -->|console integration| OSConsole[OpenShift Console<br/>ConsoleLink]
    ODHDashboard -.->|traffic routing| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>mTLS, Traffic Mgmt]

    %% Integration Points
    ODHDashboard -->|queries metrics| PrometheusQuery[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS]
    ODHDashboard -->|model metadata| ModelRegAPI[Model Registry API<br/>8080/TCP or 9090/TCP]
    ODHDashboard -.->|analytics| SegmentAnalytics[Segment Analytics<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    ODHDashboard -->|LLM distributions| LlamaStack[LlamaStack<br/>LlamaStackDistribution CR]

    %% Custom Resources Created/Managed
    subgraph CRDs["Custom Resources"]
